- Any use intended to generate advertising revenue, sponsorships, memberships, donations, or other commercial benefit

Commercial use of FreeMarket is **strictly prohibited** unless prior written permission has been obtained from the copyright holder.

Only individuals or organizations explicitly authorized in writing by the copyright holder may use FreeMarket for commercial purposes.

If you intend to use FreeMarket commercially, please contact the copyright holder before use.
